	</div>
	
	<div id="rightcol">
		<div id="right"><h1 style="font-family: &quot;arial narrow&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong> </strong></span></h1>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/images/stories/pril-07-01.jpg" border="0" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial narrow&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;">Прилавок-витрина 900х600х1200 мм</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: &quot;arial narrow&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;">цена 5700р</span></p>
<hr />
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">Готовые прилавки из алюминиевого профиля</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/images/stories/novosti/apve_sm.jpg" border="0" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">Прилавок с верхней экспозицией 900х500х900</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">цена 5080р<br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><span style="color: #333333;"> </span></span></strong></span></span></p>
<hr style="text-align: center;" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong> <img src="/images/stories/novosti/apse_sm.jpg" border="0" /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"> Прилавок со средней экспозицией 900х500х900<span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"> <br /></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">цена 5300<br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"> </span></strong></p>
<hr style="text-align: center;" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong> <img src="/images/stories/novosti/appe_sm.jpg" border="0" /></strong></p>
