<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">цена 5700</span></span></span></p>
