<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">Прилавок глухой <span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">900х500х900</span></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: arial narrow,helvetica,sans-serif;">цена 4400<br /></span></span></p>
